Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.14,0:00:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:30.21,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:36.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:44.32,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:51.53,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:01:00.34,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:05.85,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.92,0:01:10.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:15.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.94,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.11,0:01:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知自己的生日为何时 故乡为何处而长大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.38,0:01:33.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身怀命运之宝石 『蔚蓝之水』的少女娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,认识了强等人之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.45,0:01:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始了冒险之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.22,0:01:39.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于抵达故乡 非洲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 她这趟漫长的 解开身世之谜的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即将进入尾声
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:48.79,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,35 蔚蓝之水的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好大的湖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:15.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它就什么都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是娜蒂亚的故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.40,0:02:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 不要自己乱开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是娜蒂亚她…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回来啊 娜蒂亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.09,0:02:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙 强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:02:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快逃 撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么可以让娜蒂亚单独进去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.40,0:03:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝 飞行模式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 刚才不是把气球给扔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惨了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我从以前就觉得她是个怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,照这种情况看来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她是货真价实的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是受到亚特兰提斯的力量 引导着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看来像是被什么控制着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…相信娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快醒醒 娜蒂亚 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…做了个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很可怕的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨…黑色的雨持续下个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是洪水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的身体里头空空的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不停把水吸进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨一直下个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我哭喊着说不要下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:02.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是不断落下的泪水 反而让水位升高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你 玛莉还有 葛兰迪丝他们都溺水了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知不觉中变成了鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟雨水一起流入我体内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有声音传来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.68,0:05:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我害怕知道所有真相之后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自己将不再是原本的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们不是说好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要一起到你的故乡去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.73,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会永远陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家也都在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.10,0:05:48.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你什么都不需要怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好热情 好热情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:05:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可恶 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是看不见的墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,折回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都走到这里了 怎么可以回头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不 我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:10.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看看有没有别条路…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经把墙撤开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 我也要玩玩看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.25,0:06:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这颗蔚蓝之水的力量 是相当危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有继承了王家血统之人 才有办法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实在是令我吃惊连连啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连连啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的是无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:08.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已经超越人类的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我想起了那座漂流岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两者是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相同的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.52,0:07:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同样都是 古代亚特兰提斯人的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是龙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是骸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是远古的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,种类还挺多的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,远古时代的怪物们 全都被关在笼子里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里到底是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里就是 旧约圣经里出现的方舟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地球人称之为『诺亚方舟』
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地球人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是一艘船？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连这条巨大的地下通道 也是在方舟里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:56.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地上的人们 渐渐不听神的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始为所欲为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,于是神决定重新创造世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大洪水让陆地全部成为海底
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有忠实遵造神之指示的 诺亚一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及他们安置在方舟中的动物们 存活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很久很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯人起了内哄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相互怀疑 仇视
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.59,0:08:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由于过度信赖自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将一切投入至战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,陆地上一片腥风血雨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,许多生命因而牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其中一艘船发生大火沉入海中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,后人称其为亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一艘船丧失掌舵者 失去踪迹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它就是那座漂流岛 红色诺亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而最后一艘船失去飞行动力 在此坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.49,0:08:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有极少数搭乘这艘 蓝色诺亚的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:08:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才勉强幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些幸存者在这里建立了国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是你的故乡是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古代亚特兰提斯的末裔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是塔提苏司王国的 王位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也…也就是说 你是亚特兰提斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好酷喔 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成为公主可是全世界 所有女生的梦想与憧憬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是当时一切顺利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还是位公主是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且还是魔法国度的公主耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这跟你的蔚蓝之水一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.31,0:09:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我母亲留给我的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 不像你的一样 可以引发奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其实它有个很不得了的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这其实是假货
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.23,0:10:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是颗玻璃珠罢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.10,0:10:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.91,0:10:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是家里没发生事情的话 我现在还是千金小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.39,0:10:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以多少能了解你到这里来 为什么会觉得不愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我曾经回去看过以前住的大房子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发现自己中意的地方 全都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好失望呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:50.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更别说你的故乡 竟然荒凉成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:54.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 我讲话太没遮拦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你 葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.08,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是 不只是因为那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愈靠近塔提苏司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在红色诺亚那时 让我在脑海中留下的模糊记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.39,0:11:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也跟着愈来愈鲜明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 还有另一个我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在呼唤着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.83,0:11:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我复兴王族血统 取回力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这座蓝色诺亚中 我想怎样就能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里隐藏着 超乎想像的恐怖力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就等着我一声令下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我却不敢过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.05,0:11:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害怕知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我一直渴望的东西 和那股恐怖的力量有关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拥有蔚蓝之水的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藉其力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:54.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以成为神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:57.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也能成为毁灭世界的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森 请往前开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塔提苏司即将浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:12:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是水声
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:12:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,浮出水面？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.11,0:13:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.92,0:13:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.52,0:13:19.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在发抖？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刚才的废墟你也看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:29.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里头沉睡着数亿个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 求求你不要松手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.47,0:13:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些死掉之人们的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们的哀伤聚集到我体内了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么非我不可？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我会被选上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不要毁灭世界的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.46,0:14:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毁灭世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拥有蔚蓝之水 就等于得到其强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到这种景象你们还不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前支配着这里的是 破坏与死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.65,0:14:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以被影响 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.52,0:14:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要相信我哪一点？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.46,0:14:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信既任性个性又不好 只会欺负强的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信老是畏畏缩缩 只想着讨团长欢心的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,相信明明晓得是自己的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却连句再见都不肯说的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌 讨厌 全都讨厌透了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的一切都是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯一的例外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就只有我是个继承了 亚特兰提斯力量的恐怖女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:15:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,亚特兰提斯的力量 又不一定会被拿来做坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为握着钥匙的人是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.86,0:15:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是因为是我才糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然你一直说讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…我喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你一定没那么坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你很普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,国家已经消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明没有人在使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一切却都还能正常运作 好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.14,0:15:51.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,塔提苏司并没有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:54.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是换了个形式继续存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我们去把它找出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.98,0:15:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新亚特兰提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.68,0:16:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是新亚特兰提斯的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:10.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正如石像鬼所说的 我是『娜蒂亚公主』
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然很可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我跟那些人是同类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.47,0:16:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,王宫的中心地带 巴别塔前端
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.94,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:32.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是我的故乡 塔提苏司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,变成岛屿了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前 艾丽朵拉也曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,巴别塔真正的用意 到底是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通讯器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,通讯？跟哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我们真正的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利用光传递
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,故乡？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里…塔提苏司不就是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是跟『真正的故乡』
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就位在距离这里 277.5光年的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光…光年？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是长度的单位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,277.5光年就表示
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以光的速度前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,得花277又半年 才能抵达的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光的速度？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:24.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1秒可以前进30万公里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么远的距离 不就是其它星球…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…亚特兰提斯的… 塔提苏司的人们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:44.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是来自宇宙的其它星球
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我并不是地球人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.29,0:17:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,身上流的是来自外星的血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好好看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本就不普通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我会让你不幸 让大家不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总有一天还会让不幸 遍布全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像爸爸和石像鬼一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.41,0:18:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,藉由蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 是我 你认得出来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.32,0:18:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我好害怕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:13.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.42,0:19:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以欺负娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我刚刚究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.10,0:19:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蔚蓝之水又发光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的身体愈接近地面 速度也跟着减弱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像是被一双 看不见的手支撑着似的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,慢慢着地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:20:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终究还是无法逃离命运 逃离蔚蓝之水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你以为自己是悲剧女主角吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你晓得大家有多为你担心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.80,0:20:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真想让你看看 刚才强是多么惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我没关系的 桑森
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你为什么有办法活下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我现在活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要活下去…就有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论蔚蓝之水的秘密是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.09,0:20:38.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不论与亚特兰提斯 有着怎样的关联
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.43,0:20:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算不是地球人 又有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起 强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上头好像有刻了字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火龙与南面贡德之月日 第15次的复活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.16,0:21:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天 这个值得庆贺的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愿吾之爱女娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能得百倍的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千倍的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.07,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及万倍的慈爱眷顾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在此留下其生命记录
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吾之爱女娜蒂亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我出生时的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为我立下的碑文
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.69,0:21:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上面说的什么月日 指的是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,换算成公元就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1875年5月31日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.86,0:21:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,5月31日…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不就是今天吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那今天不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚的生日！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生日？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.75,0:22:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太棒了 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.75,0:22:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,终于晓得你的生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.45,0:22:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晓得你出生的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…出生的日子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.43,0:22:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生日快乐 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生日快乐 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生日快乐 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.57,0:22:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.22,0:22:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝你生日快乐 亲爱的娜蒂亚\N强 还有大家…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.70,0:22:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.27,0:23:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,75年出生就表示 你已经15岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.78,0:23:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一直很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.38,0:23:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,担心什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.25,0:23:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,担心你的母亲知道 戒指的宝石其实是假的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想她一定早就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.53,0:23:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却还是小心翼翼地珍藏着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.16,0:23:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:33.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,母亲说因为那是爸爸 第一次送她的宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以很珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.74,0:23:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我觉得就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我现在想要这么相信着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.65,0:23:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.02,0:23:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到上面去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是…\N那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:54.55,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:24:02.55,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.63,0:24:07.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.77,0:24:12.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:20.44,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:31.05,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.12,0:24:39.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.03,0:24:44.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:48.73,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:57.91,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.63,0:25:09.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好久不见了 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.73,0:25:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿着蔚蓝之水乖乖走出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.60,0:25:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你这么做 你的朋友们就能保住性命
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.30,0:25:18.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.87,0:25:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚主动走到石像鬼面前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.41,0:25:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是石像鬼却食言 对我们发动攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.15,0:25:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.61,0:25:29.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『万能战舰新鹦鹉螺号』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.25,0:25:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
